    <note>Yang(2) Shen [16594] Opposed the new policies when Wang(2) Anshi [1762] took control of the government and was prefect of Jizhou (Shandong) and retired. Thus, active in ca. 1070. His ancestors moved from Jizhou, Jian-s to Linjiang and therefore probably related to Yang(2) Wanli's [10566] lineage. His kinship with his great great grandson, Xie [23485], established in Linjiang FZ, 12.8a. Linjiang FZ, 12.2b; Jiangxi TZ, 21.11b. CBD, 4, 3100.</note>
